{"tid":1678610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班仆街影人大頭，你班左膠成日話夠？？？？？？","createTime":"2019-10-27T17:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T18:12:53.000Z","uid":232845,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f617e62b4790b20bb5d28ea8a2647665e6c7909e","tid":1678610,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:33:30.000Z","msg":"TO 左膠<br />\n<br />\n知唔知幾撚多人俾班臭閪影大頭搞到拉撚左？<br />\n你班仆街左膠仲話夠夠夠會死人？<br />\n拉撚左果Ｄ有冇死到都唔撚知呀！<br />\n佢一條仆街影幾十個人，一交俾班狗，搵夠料就拉人<br />\n你地仲要俾佢走？<br />\n下次見到你班左膠再出黎，我見到一定幫你地理髮！<br />\n<br />\nFROM 理髮師"},{"pid":"375337459425edc46b7fc622461f905e00760256","tid":1678610,"uid":232845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"屌撚你班左膠"},{"pid":"7d580a1c14008ef45fb22e40826dbcc95ac0b700","tid":1678610,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"同路人，請幫手捉住班左膠<br />\n唔需要用武力對佢地，等理髮師出手處理下就夠"},{"pid":"7d07484328567fc0d26878975dce56fd966a97ea","tid":1678610,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"73f669760327b4b54cb5e0fee260169156298a5b","tid":1678610,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"大頭照上傳後 <br />\n兄弟就要去大煙區囉!<br />\n所以成日: 夠啦夠啦 <br />\n係講緊大煙區夠人呀?<br />\n定係佢唔會再影架啦，因為影夠？"},{"pid":"f1163353bd4291bd8b9470cb82f0b26594b6bd59","tid":1678610,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T17:48:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4frL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=d154878f\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4frL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=45bc7bf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4frL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=da15efec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"d0c964775eb44115a0e1fd2f6c8aa091f6a4d0bd","tid":16786